<p>
Layouts and Line Drawings provides a REST-style feed of yacht specfications, layouts,
and line drawings.  We return two objects: Specification, Photo.  Each comes in two forms:

 <ul>
 <li>An efficient limited version when we return a plurality of the objects</li>
 <li>The complete version when we return a singular object</li>
 </ul>
</p>

<h3>Schema</h3>
<p>

The objects have the following versions.

The limited versions are:
<div class="code">
<div class="left">
Specification
  id:integer
  thumb:string
  length:integer
  manufacturer:string
  model:string
  year:integer
</div>
<div class="right">
Photo
  specification_id:integer
  id:integer
  full:string
  thumb:string
</div>
</div>
</p>

<p style="clear: both;">
The complete versions are:
